Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.72,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（タラオ）\Nここより外は そりゃあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:34.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course there's an outside beyond here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:39.22,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,先生たち専用のドアの向こうが\Nどうなってるか僕らは知らないし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.72,0:01:39.22,Main,,0,0,0,,We don't know what happens\Nbehind the teachers' doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:42.91,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,配膳が下げられていく先も\N通気口の中も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,or where our food comes from,\Nor what's inside the vents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そういうスペースも\N考えようによっては外だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:46.58,Main,,0,0,0,,All these gaps\Nmake me think of an "outside."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.47,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（トキオ）ミミヒメは なんで外に\N行きたがってるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would Mimihime want to go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:54.05,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,トキオはミミヒメが好きなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you like Mimihime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:55.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そりゃまあ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.12,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そう…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:58.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:01:59.85,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うっ　いっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.14,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:02.98,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（タラオ）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.63,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕 そろそろ部屋に戻る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:07.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（トキオ）送る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,-I'll come with you.\N-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:11.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（タラオ）いい自動操縦で帰るから\N心配要らない…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:11.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll use the auto-drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:15.74,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（イワ･ナナキ）ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:20.03,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（イワ･ナナキ）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,へへっ ふふっ ハハハッ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.56,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（イワ･ナナキの笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:27.81,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（クク）くくっ\N（トキオ）はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:29.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ククの笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.74,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（クク）えへっ\N（トキオ）クク その絵！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuku, that drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.82,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,コナにもらったんだ　いいでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Kona gave it to me. Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.38,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（トキオ）返せ！ うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Give it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.07,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（クク）\Nなんでだ！ 僕がもらったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? He gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:40.54,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（トキオ）コナの絵は\N僕がもらう約束してたんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Kona promised to give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ずるいぞ！ トキオばっかり！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,No fair! You get them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:46.51,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕もコナの絵が好きなんだもん\Nもらったっていいじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:46.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I like Kona's drawings, too.\NWhy can't I get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（トキオ）それも… そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.11,Main,,0,0,0,,-You're right.\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.11,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.18,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（トキオ）ごめん クク…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.53,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,クッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.56,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ミミヒメ）ん…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.69,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ちょ…！ わあ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:02.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ちょーい！ 何この扱いは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:02.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.87,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（トキオ）\Nなんでククにあげちゃったのさ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did you give it to Kuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:05.87,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.41,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,約束してたじゃないか…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（コナ）今度はトキオのために描く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll draw the next one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.88,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,本当？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:12.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（トキオ）僕はコナが\N想像するものが好きなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I like the things you imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:20.24,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ミミヒメ）\Nまったく トキオは泣き虫だな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez. Tokio is such a crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.34,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ククに絵を取られたくらいで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Just because Kuku got that drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:25.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（シャワーを止める音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.85,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ドアの開閉音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.35,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.14,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（メールの着信音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:31.18,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（シロ）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.26,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ミミヒメからメール？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:35.26,Main,,0,0,0,,A message from Mimihime?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.65,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あっ！ えっ うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.36,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はあ… はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,フフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:54.76,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,<c.dssshr0>（キルコの寝息）</c>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.61,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）はあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハア… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:01.10,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわ… びっしょびしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.10,Main,,0,0,0,,So sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:03.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（窓に張り付く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:06.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,は…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:10.47,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,起きろマル！ 人食い… ヒルコだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Maru. It's the Man-eater, Hiruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.34,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,だめだ 閉められてる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.34,Main,,0,0,0,,No good. It's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.85,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,風呂から出るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll go out through the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.59,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）ああ～…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.43,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）しゃっきりしろ\N（マル）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:29.82,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,睡眠薬か何か盛られた\N僕らは眠らされてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:29.83,Main,,0,0,0,,She fed us some sort of drug\Nto put us to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:31.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（<ruby>女将<rt>おかみ</rt></ruby>）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.12,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うっ！　ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.49,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あんたたち\N危ないから中にいなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,You two! It's dangerous. Get back inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:41.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）だから僕たち\Nそいつ殺せますから！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you we can kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.89,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,は…　あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:45.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（屋根で物音）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,キル光線は？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,The Kiru-Beam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,いつでも撃てる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Fully charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,-There!\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）あっちだ！\N（女将）ハッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.16,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）うわあ！ ちょっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.78,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）大丈夫！ 転んだだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm okay. Just tripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.29,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ふう…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:22.19,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（近づく不気味な音）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:24.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）うっ… はっ\N（キルコ）はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.12,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）なんだ今の？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.43,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）マル 何か投げてみて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Maru, try throwing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.04,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,オーケー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.21,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわっ！ 超音波か？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.21,Main,,0,0,0,,An ultrasonic blast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:36.64,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,いや 何かチラチラ見える
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I see something flickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.56,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,これ 鳴き声じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not the sound of its voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:43.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ムチみたいなものを\N振り回してる音だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the sound of its whip things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.68,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル･キルコ）ハア… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,おなかの腕から３本\Nムチが生えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,There are three whips on each arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:02.03,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あれを潰さないと俺は近づけない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't get close unless we destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:06.71,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）３本か…\N羽根も止めたいし 弾足りるかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:04.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Three? Gotta get the wings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Are there enough bullets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.16,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,いや… ３ ３で６本だからね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,No, three and three makes six.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.42,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）分かってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.34,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.50,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あいつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル･キルコ）わあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハアハアハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,こっちだ！ ハアハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:19.81,Main,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.53,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.22,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:30.64,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）よーし！ 片腕と\Nついでに羽根にも当ててきた！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:30.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I hit an arm and a wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:31.89,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）天才！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:31.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What a sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\Nこっちの射程のほうが少し長い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,The gun's range\Nis a bit longer than the whips.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:38.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,また近づけば もう１本の腕も潰す
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:38.90,Main,,0,0,0,,If I can get a bit closer,\NI can hit the other arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.69,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そしたらマル君いけるでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you can go after it, Maru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,-Okay.\N-Here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.15,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）よーし！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:46.36,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）距離を誤ると\N腕がなくなるから 気をつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:46.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll lose an arm if you get too close.\NBe careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:49.83,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）うっ はあ…\Nなるべく考えたくなかったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I was trying not to think about that…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:50.97,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:50.97,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（物音）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:05.24,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ヒルコの足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.54,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はあ… はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:17.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ここだ！　うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.07,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）女将さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,The manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（女将）逃げて！ 逃げなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Run! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.44,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（空撃ちの音）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:28.64,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（女将）\Nもうやめて　私の息子なの！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:28.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop! That's my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\N子供をあれに食われたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,So your son was eaten by that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.10,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（女将）違う！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,No. Yuto went inside it,\Nand it became Yuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:37.21,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,<ruby>悠人<rt>ゆうと</rt></ruby>はあの中に入って\Nあれが悠人になったんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.05,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,なっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:43.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）そうか 人食いを\N守るために僕らは眠らされたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:43.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You drugged us to protect the Man-eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:46.65,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕は食われかけたことが\Nあるから分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:46.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I was almost eaten by one, so I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:50.91,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あいつは獲物を\N粉々に分解して吸収する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:50.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It cuts up its prey and absorbs them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:54.10,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,食われた人間が\N主体になれるとは思えない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:54.10,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm sorry, I don't think those\Nwho are eaten take over its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:57.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,でも あれは悠人なの！\N守ってくれてる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,But that is Yuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:57.92,Main,,0,0,0,,He protects me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:02.49,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,私に乱暴しようとしたヤツらから\N助けてくれたこともあったの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,He even rescued me when I was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.15,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:08.45,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:10.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,どっちにしても戦う手段がないし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm out of shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.89,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,危険がないなら殺す必要もないか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:13.89,Main,,0,0,0,,If it's not a threat,\Nthere's no reason to kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:15.53,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（女将）ホッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:18.89,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,悠人！ この人たちも\N分かってくれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:18.89,Main,,0,0,0,,They understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.35,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,私は大丈夫だから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）意思疎通… できてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,They can communicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ほら ね？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.54,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,くくっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.66,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ああ…！ くそっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.27,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）気づいたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:48.38,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）あのムチ\N一方向にしか振れないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,The whip only swings in one direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,つまり 一撃かわせば隙ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,So there's a pause between attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:55.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あんた 人が目の前で\N殺されてんのに！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:55.30,Main,,0,0,0,,How can you think like that?\NSomeone just died!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:00.80,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）そうしないと\N生きていけないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:09:00.81,Main,,0,0,0,,If I don't, we won't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.85,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:08.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あいつ 殺してくる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:08.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.54,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マルの息を吐く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,フッ ハ… ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,くわっ！ くっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:37.43,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,入れ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:37.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I got in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:46.61,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.34,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）\Nヒルコは なんで昨日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:02.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Why didn't Hiruko attack\Nthe manager until yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:02.45,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,女将さんに\N手を出さなかったんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:07.09,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）本当に子供の人格が\N残っていたのかもしれないし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was her son's consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:10.00,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,本能的に\N生かしておいたのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,or it instinctively kept her alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.25,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）\N宿にエサが寄ってくるからか…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Since its prey gathers around this place…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.65,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）もしかしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:18.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe she fed the guests to her son…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.54,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,女将さんが息子に\N客を食わせていたから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:19.45,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:23.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）はあ やめとこ\N真相は闇の中でいい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.06,Main,,0,0,0,,The truth can stay hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.35,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ただでさえ\N大変な案件を抱えてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.35,Main,,0,0,0,,We already have enough on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.15,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,天国を探す なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Looking for "Heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ああ 電池持ってく？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, the batteries. Want to take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:35.66,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あれは女将さんにあげたものだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't you give them to the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,フッ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.33,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,わっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.24,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）なんだよ やめろよ～\N（キルコ）フフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:42.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:48.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）お姉ちゃん\N動いてる電車に乗ったことあるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:48.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Sis, have you ever ridden a moving train?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:51.05,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\N大災害の時 ３歳だったからなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:51.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I was three during the Great Disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:53.50,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,乗ってたとしても覚えてないや
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't remember even if I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.95,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あれ？ お姉ちゃん20歳だったら\N当時は５歳じゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.95,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're 20, then you were five--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.51,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ちょっと！ その水 大丈夫なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that water safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）ぺっ…\N口すすぐだけなら大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.58,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I'm just rinsing my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.47,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,変な味しないし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Plus, it doesn't taste weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,いい天気だね～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:07.94,Main,,0,0,0,,It's such a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.39,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,船出にはもってこいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Perfect for sailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,KIRUKO-MARU
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.24,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,下行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:30.07,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）うわあ！ いかん！\N思ったより頼んない これ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's shakier than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:33.90,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわあ！ そっと乗れ！\N羽のようにふわりと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:32.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Get on gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Step like a feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.55,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）無理言うな！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.55,Main,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:40.05,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）やった！\Nなんとか浮かんでるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:40.05,Main,,0,0,0,,It's floating somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:45.66,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,盗賊どもの話が本当なら\Nもう鼻の先だ トマト天国
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:45.66,Main,,0,0,0,,If those old guys were telling the truth,\NTomato Heaven is right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:51.73,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）スゥ… 今更なんだけど\Nサメとかワニとかいないだろうね？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Kind of late to ask, but there aren't\Nany sharks or crocodiles, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.28,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,知らん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.26,Main,,0,0,0,,-Don't know.\N-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:56.26,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）おーい！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,俺が殺せるのは\Nヒルコだけだからね！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.93,Main,,0,0,0,,The only thing I can kill is Hiruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:02.14,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,もしワニがわーっときたら\Nお姉ちゃんがなんとかしないと！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,You gotta do something if a croc shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.27,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）マ… マルが全部\N食われるまでには 何か考える
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I-- I'll think of something\Nbefore you get eaten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:08.07,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）ひと口も食わすなよ！\Nボディガードだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't let it bite me.\NYou're the bodyguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:13.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）ていうか 俺がワニなら\Nお姉ちゃんを先に食べるね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:13.02,Main,,0,0,0,,If I was a crocodile, I'd eat you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.67,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）ハアハア…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.84,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,こげ！ 全力でこぐんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.84,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）ハア… ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Row! Go all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.32,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,向こう岸までは\N大した距離じゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:23.68,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マルの息切れ）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:22.84,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,肉食が来ないことを祈って\Nこぐんだー！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:22.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Just keep praying\Nthat a carnivore doesn't show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ボールが転がる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ミミヒメ）ごめんごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.27,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（トキオ）大丈夫 僕が取ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:30.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（走る足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.10,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ハア… あっ　は…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.60,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,<c.dssshr0>（トキオ）先生たち用のドア</c>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:37.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The teachers-only door.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:41.49,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,<c.dssshr0>この向こうが… 外？</c>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:41.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is the outside behind it?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:46.18,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,<c.dssshr0>あの… ボールが 　　</c>\N<c.dssshr0>そこに入ってしまって</c>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:46.18,Main,,0,0,0,,The ball went over there…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.45,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,<c.dssshr0>（ロボット音声） 　　　</c>\N<c.dssshr0>　どうぞ 取ってください</c>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go ahead and take it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.71,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.71,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（何かを蹴る音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:01.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（タカ）\Nおっ！ あったあった　へっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.71,Main,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,よーし くっつけ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, stick there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.54,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（アンズ）\N本当にやる気？ 危ないって！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:07.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to do it?\NIt's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.45,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（タカ） へへっ これがさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to test how strong this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:12.54,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,どれくらい力が出るのか\N実験するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.73,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（アンズ）壊したら絶対怒られるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.73,Main,,0,0,0,,They'll get mad if you break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.18,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（タカ）大丈夫だって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:17.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I said it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:21.15,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,それでは 大実験開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll begin the great experiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.82,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,おっ おおっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.48,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ミチカ）うわあ！ すげえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:28.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.61,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（アンズ）\Nあんな所まで 行っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It's going so high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.95,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,こりゃ 上まで届きそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,At this rate, it'll go all the way up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.83,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわ！ おっ ちょ ちょ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Hold--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.38,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うわあ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.63,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（一同）きゃあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.71,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（タカ）うっ…　うう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,くっ… いってえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.59,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ミミヒメ）ハア…\N（シロ）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:51.98,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ミミヒメ）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:53.98,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ああ… ええ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.71,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ミチカ）\Nなんでシロが血 出てんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is Shiro the one bleeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（一同の笑い）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.88,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.28,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うーん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,まだ何か落ちてきそうな…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling\Nsomething else is going to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:10.43,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）ここが天国なら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:11.29,Main,,0,0,0,,If this is "Heaven,"\Nthen my job ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,これにてお役ごめんなんだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:17.98,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,問題は君自身が天国の場所も
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:20.44,Main,,0,0,0,,But you don't know where "Heaven" is,\Nor what you'll do when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.65,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そこで何をするのかも\N知らないことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.80,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:24.32,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\Nつまり 君が納得しない限り
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:26.47,Main,,0,0,0,,So my job doesn't end\Nuntil you're satisfied with the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.46,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ガードの仕事が終わんないわけ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:31.76,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,できる限りのことはしたいからさ\N心当たりは隠さず話してよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:31.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do everything I can,\Nso don't keep any secrets from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）\N何も隠してるつもりはないんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not hiding anything, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:35.74,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ジッパーの音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:36.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）これ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:36.94,Main,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.72,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.23,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）その筒の中に\Nクスリと注射器が入ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.23,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a needle and a drug\Ninside this cylinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:47.74,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a guy with the same face as me\Nout there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:47.74,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,俺と同じ顔をしたヤツが\Nどこかにもう１人いる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:52.28,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そいつを見つけたら\Nこのクスリを打つように言われてた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I was told to inject him with this drug\Nwhen I find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:56.87,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,だから 天国には\N俺と同じ顔のヤツがいるんだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:56.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I believe that the person I'm looking for,\Nis in this place called "Heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）打つと どうなる？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.00,Main,,0,0,0,,And after the shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:02.26,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）さあ？ 病気が治るとか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:02.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't know. He'll get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:06.46,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,とにかく 俺が行けばみんなが\N助かるかもしれないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:06.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I was told it would help everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,それ以外は特に知らされてないなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.76,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんは何も聞いてないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:12.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Did she tell you anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.89,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,最後にミクラさんと一緒にいたの\Nお姉ちゃんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:16.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You were the last one to see Mikura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.64,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ミクラ）ハア… めくって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:20.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Pull it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.48,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:28.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（ミクラ）これでマルを… 守って
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:28.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Protect Maru with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.33,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）分かった！\Nどこまで連れていけばいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I will. Where should I take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hea…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.46,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,て…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:39.91,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）僕も 君を天国へ\N連れて行くとしか…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:39.91,Main,,0,0,0,,She only told me to take you to "Heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.20,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人１）\N何してるの？ あんたたち
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:42.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.09,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）あ… こんちわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:47.36,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人２）\N盗賊の類いでは なさそうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:47.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't look like bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.74,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,この辺りの人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you locals?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:52.74,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あ いやあ…\N東京の方からずーっと歩いて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:52.74,Main,,0,0,0,,No, we walked all the way from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人２）それで偶然ここへ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:56.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人たちの笑い）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.62,Main,,0,0,0,,And you found us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.25,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\N一応場所は教わって来ました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Someone told us about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.33,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,天国みたいなとこだと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like "Heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.31,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人３）\Nじゃあ知ってて来たんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,So you came here on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人１）移住希望ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:05.47,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\N場合によっては この子が…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:05.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You see, this kid is--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:08.66,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人１）それじゃ とにかく\N園長のところへ連れてってあげて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:08.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's take them to the Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:11.41,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人３）こっちだ　入ってきな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.41,Main,,0,0,0,,This way. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:14.12,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（子供たちのはしゃぐ声）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,-Taisuke!\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.80,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住民）\N東京から来たっつーことは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're from Tokyo,\Nthen you climbed down the big fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.85,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,大断層降りてきたんかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.50,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）\Nああ あのダーンってなった崖？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that huge cliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.56,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）苦労しましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It was so tiring.\NWe made a raft and crossed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.86,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,イカダ的なやつを作って\N渡ってきました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.34,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住民）ハッハハハハハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:31.25,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,危ねえな！\Nイリエワニとかウヨウヨいたろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.86,Main,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Saltwater crocs swim in those waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.01,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル･キルコ）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.70,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）いたんじゃん！\Nワニいたんじゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.70,Main,,0,0,0,,There were crocs. Crocs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.16,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\Nかっ かまれなかったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You weren't eaten so don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.62,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,考えるのはよそうよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:41.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住民）ハッハハハハハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:43.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（<ruby>草壁<rt>くさかべ</rt></ruby>）\Nこの集落を仕切ってる草壁です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:43.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Kusakabe, the leader of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,こっちは妻の<ruby>桃子<rt>ももこ</rt></ruby>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my wife, Momoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:50.86,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（桃子）まあ ご覧になった\Nとおりの集まりでして
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.86,Main,,0,0,0,,As you see, we're just a rag-tag bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:54.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,前の文明にすがりついて\N生きていくとか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We tried to cling to the past,{\i}\N{\i1}and dreamt of reviving our society,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:57.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,できもしない復興を夢見るとか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:59.87,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そんなのが\N嫌になっちゃった人たちがね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but many people grew tired{\i}\N{\i1}of such futile hopes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.56,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,自然の中で実ったものだけを\Nいただくという
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So we chose a simple life,{\i}\N{\i1}living off the fruits of the earth.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:06.63,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,シンプルな生き方を\Nすることにしたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:10.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（草壁）最初は父たちと\N数人の畑作りだったんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was just my father and a few farmers,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.89,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,いつの間にか大所帯になりました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but we soon became this large family.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,わあ～！ いいですね！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow. That's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.21,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）んん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:20.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,トマトの天国だって聞いたんですが\Nここのことで合ってます？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard this is "Tomato Heaven,"\Nis that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:24.42,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ああ！\N以前はトマトだらけだったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It used to be full of tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.96,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,今は土地に適したものが\N色々とれますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Now we can grow all kinds of local crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（煙を吐く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人たちの話し声）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:36.03,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）いい所だね～　トマト天国
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Tomato Heaven is such a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.53,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,この規模の農場はすごいと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,A farm this size is amazing,\Nbut something feels off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.29,0:17:42.25,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,なんかいびつだな～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ご飯まで出してもらってアレだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:45.37,Main,,0,0,0,,They are nice enough to feed us, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.82,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）うん\Nお姉ちゃんがそう思うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if you think so, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:50.78,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,自分の意見を持ちなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:50.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Make your own opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:54.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人たちの笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:55.15,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）誰もマルの顔に\N反応しないってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Since no one's reacting to your face,\NI guess that look-alike guy isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.01,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ここにはいないんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.29,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そっくりなヤツ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:01.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あっ！ そうか\Nそういう探し方もあるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, that's one way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:05.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,おいおい！ 今までに\N見落としてるんじゃないだろうな～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:05.75,Main,,0,0,0,,As if, did you not realize that\Nthis entire time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人）あ！その顔！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,That face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:11.61,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あんた <ruby>竹早<rt>たけはや</rt></ruby><ruby>桐子<rt>きりこ</rt></ruby>さんだよな！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:11.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You're Kiriko Takehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.06,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）あ…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.60,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,電力車レースの！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:13.61,Main,,0,0,0,,The electro-kart racer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:16.05,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,いや 人違いです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:16.05,Main,,0,0,0,,No, you got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:21.25,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人）俺 大ファンだったんだよ\Nほら 今でもブロマイド持ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:21.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I was a huge fan.\NLook, I still have your photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:25.87,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,もう何年経つかな～\N急にいなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,How long since you disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:28.83,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,５年？ 心配したよ～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:28.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Five years? I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:33.78,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,レース中に弟ひき殺して\N気が触れたなんて噂もあったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,There were rumors that you lost it\Nafter killing your brother in a race.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:34.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）おい！\N（住人）うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:34.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.54,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,全然似てね…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn't look--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うーん…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:45.33,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）\N似てるかもしれないけど別人だって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:45.33,Main,,0,0,0,,They might look alike, but that's not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:46.33,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,いやでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:48.57,Main,,0,0,0,,-But--\N-I said you got the wrong person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:48.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,人違いだっつってんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.82,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,し… 失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.82,Main,,0,0,0,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:52.63,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）ん？ 待って！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:53.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住民）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:54.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,今 何か…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I just…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,これだ！ お姉ちゃん 見覚えない？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.79,Main,,0,0,0,,This! Sis, doesn't this look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:04.35,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ん～？ あるような ないような…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:04.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe, maybe not…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）分かった　ここだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I got it! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:06.63,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）ふんっ！\N（マル）ぐえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:09.84,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,人の下半身をまさぐるのではない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't go around groping someone's leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.75,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）ちがっ… これだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.75,Main,,0,0,0,,No, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.13,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you get this box?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:19.97,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,この箱 どこから来たの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:26.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住人たちの笑い声）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.84,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（住民）さあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:21.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:26.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,東京と船が行き来しててさ\N野菜出荷したり色々あるから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,We're always taking vegetables\Nand stuff to Tokyo on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:30.40,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,使える箱なら色んな所から\N行ったり来たりするんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Boxes like this can come from anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:34.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）船で東京と\Nつながってんのか　すごいな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:33.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You can get to Tokyo by ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:34.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:38.82,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）このマークを追うと\Nマルと何かつながってこないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:38.82,Main,,0,0,0,,If we look into this logo,\Nwon't we find a connection to you, Maru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:43.07,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,少なくとも\Nこれの正体は分かるかもなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:43.07,Main,,0,0,0,,At least, we'll find out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:48.02,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you know\Nof a place called "Heaven"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:48.02,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ちなみにお兄さん\N天国という場所に心当たりは？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:48.97,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そりゃここ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,-Right here.\N-Other than here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:49.94,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ここ以外で！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:53.00,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,え？ う～ん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,フッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:58.92,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,竹早桐子ちゃんがいた頃の\N浅草かなあ～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:58.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Asakusa during Kiriko Takehaya's era.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.10,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:03.38,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ありがとう お兄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:03.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.22,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,握手握手っ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,That helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:09.41,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\Nもう少し聞き込みしてダメだったら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:12.13,Main,,0,0,0,,If we don't get any more information,\Nlet's get on the ship back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:12.13,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,船に乗せてもらって東京に戻ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:13.21,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:13.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.73,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,思ってたより日本は広かった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Japan is much bigger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:19.86,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,このまま探してても\N永久に天国は見つからん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll never find "Heaven" this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:23.12,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ここまで来て\Nまた戻るのはシャクだが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:23.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a waste to go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:27.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,君の素性を探るほうが\N天国への近道だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:27.58,Main,,0,0,0,,but if we investigate your background,\NI think we'll get to Heaven faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:34.03,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\Nあったあった！ イモ 食べる？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:34.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Found some potatoes! Want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.26,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,１本ぐらいバレないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,They won't know if one is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:40.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,どうした？ 元気ない　酔った？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:40.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong?{\i}\N{\i1}You don't look good. Seasick?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:46.14,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,天国はもういいよ\N見つかる気もしないし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Forget about Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.14,Main,,0,0,0,,We won't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:50.04,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,俺 お姉ちゃんと畑で暮らしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to live on the farm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.10,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕はやだよ あんな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:56.72,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,昼は畑を耕して\N夜は大麻吸って騒いで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:56.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Farming all day and getting high at night…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:59.80,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,何が自然だよ\Nアッパラパーの集まりじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:59.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What nature? It's just a bunch of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:01.51,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,そうじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:04.79,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,なんならお姉ちゃんの便利屋を\N手伝ってもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:04.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I could help you with your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.87,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,俺… お姉ちゃんが好きだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I-- I like you, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.08,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:11.95,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:15.52,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）\Nや… ややや… 君 君！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:19.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Confessing in such a place\Ndoesn't do either of us any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.52,0:21:17.48,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,こんな逃げ場のないところで\N告白するのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.01,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,お互いのためによくないぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:22.38,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,真面目に言ってるんだ！\N真面目に答えろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Give me a serious answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:24.71,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル･キルコ）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:29.37,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（キルコ）わっ ちょちょちょ！\N一旦離れて！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, stop! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:30.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,無理やりは…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:30.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Forcing is--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.77,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,（マル）\Nうっ… ごごごご… ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:34.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so, so, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ううん ありがとうね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:37.94,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Thanks, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:43.43,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,あのね 僕も真面目に\N話すから聞いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:43.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm going to tell you something.\NSo listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:44.57,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.51,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,突拍子もないこと言うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:50.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It might be crazy, but I'm being serious,\Nso I want you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:50.99,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,真面目に言ってるんだから\Nそこは分かってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:55.58,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,僕 この体は女なんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,My body is a woman's,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:22:01.33,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,こっちの つまり脳みそが男なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:22:01.34,Main,,0,0,0,,but in here, my mind is a man's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.30,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,は…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:07.18,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,だから 僕 男なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,So… I'm a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:10.93,Main - Jpn,,0,0,0,,はえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:10.93,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
